title: Ep 189: Embrace Your Age with Maye Musk

description:
Model and nutritionist Maye Musk, 71, opens up about ageism in fashion, her time as a plus-size model, her divorce, working with CoverGirl, and so much more. Before the interview, Jenn and Jess share the week's beauty news (Perso, baby Yoda makeup, Taraji P. Henson's TPH Hair, Charlotte Tilbury sale rumors); Jenn takes us on her Invisalign journey; and we offer tips and suggest shampoos and conditioners for fine, frizzy hair. Also in this episode: beauty tips, braces, orthodontics, fine hair, frizzy hair, nutrition advice, and more.
